##
127.0.0.1	localhost
255.255.255.255	broadcasthost
::1             localhost 
fe80::1%lo0	localhost
192.168.1.10	homestead.test
192.168.2.10	hackerpair.test
<mark>127.0.0.1	lsapp.dev</mark>
</pre>

